## Backend API — All Endpoints

### Auth (Supabase — not Django)
- Login/logout handled by @supabase/supabase-js
- After login call GET /api/users/me/ to load the user profile into Zustand

### Users  GET/POST /api/users/
- GET /api/users/me/
- GET /api/users/                      admin only, ?role=
- POST /api/users/                     admin only
- PATCH /api/users/<id>/role/          admin only
- PATCH /api/users/<id>/               admin or self

### Clinic
- GET/POST   /api/clinic/patients/
- GET/PATCH  /api/clinic/patients/<id>/
- GET/POST   /api/clinic/visits/
- GET/PATCH  /api/clinic/visits/<id>/
- GET/POST   /api/clinic/consultations/
- GET        /api/clinic/consultations/<id>/

### Lab
- GET/POST   /api/lab/tests/           GET: any | POST: admin
- GET/PATCH  /api/lab/tests/<id>/
- GET/POST   /api/lab/orders/          GET: any | POST: doctor
- GET/PATCH  /api/lab/orders/<id>/     PATCH: lab_tech, admin
- GET/POST   /api/lab/results/         GET: any | POST: lab_tech
- GET        /api/lab/results/<id>/

### Billing
- GET/POST   /api/billing/invoices/                          ?visit_id= ?status= ?patient_id=
- GET        /api/billing/invoices/<id>/
- POST       /api/billing/invoices/<id>/items/               add line item
- DELETE     /api/billing/invoices/<id>/items/<item_id>/
- POST       /api/billing/invoices/<id>/finalize/            { discount_amount, notes }
- POST       /api/billing/invoices/<id>/void/                { void_reason } — admin only
- POST       /api/billing/invoices/<id>/pay/                 Chapa → returns { checkout_url, qr_code }
- POST       /api/billing/invoices/<id>/pay-cash/            instant cash payment
- GET        /api/billing/invoices/<id>/payments/
- POST       /api/billing/webhook/chapa/                     no auth — HMAC verified server-side

### Queue / Patient Flow
