### Queue state machine — valid transitions only
checked_in → waiting → called → in_progress → completed
called → no_show
no_show → waiting (reinsert)
// Never show an action button for an invalid transition.

### Billing flow
// Invoice lifecycle: draft → (add line items) → finalize → pay
// Pay returns { checkout_url, qr_code } — render qr_code as <img src={qr_code} />
// Cash payment via /pay-cash/ — no redirect needed
// Void is admin-only — gate behind hasPermission('void_invoice')

## Code Style
- Functional components only, no class components
- Every component and hook has explicit TypeScript return types
- Use named exports, not default exports for components (except pages)
- Zod schemas live next to their form component
- Never use `any` — use `unknown` then narrow
- Format currency as ETB: `new Intl.NumberFormat('am-ET', { style: 'currency', currency: 'ETB' }).format(amount)`
- All dates via date-fns: `format(parseISO(dateString), 'dd MMM yyyy, HH:mm')`
- Error boundaries on every page
- All mutations show a toast on success and on error (use shadcn/ui Toaster)
